<section class="post-content">
  
      <h1 id="what-a-colorful-post">What a colorful post!</h1>

<p>This is an idea that came from <a href="https://github.com/xukimseven/HardCandy-Jekyll">xukimseven/HardCandy-Jekyll</a> 
